	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />WROM = Writable ROM?
<br />
<br />Threaded bank-switching = mapper keeps track of multiple threads of execution and switches banks automatically during a context switch? (not sure how it would make much of a difference in the work required to switch contexts; see <a href="http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?t=1292" class="postlink">Multithreading Demo</a>).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


